properties.areaDesc: Waters from Cape Mendocino to Pt. Arena CA from 10 to 60 nm; Coastal waters from Cape Mendocino to Pt. Arena CA out 10 nm
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 6 at 2:25PM PST until January 9 at 3:00AM PST by NWS Eureka CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...South winds 10 to 20 kt on Tuesday becoming northwest 10
to 15 kt Tuesday night. Seas NW 9 to 12 feet expected.

* WHERE...Cape Mendocino to Pt Arena out 10 nm and Cape
Mendocino to Pt Arena 10 to 60 nm.

* WHEN...From 1 PM Tuesday to 3 AM PST Thursday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 1 PM TUESDAY TO 3 AM PST THURSDAY
